      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone looking for a budget-friendly ride. While the engine and transmission are functional, the car shows noticeable signs of age, including some scratches and minor dents on the exterior and visible wear on the interior upholstery. It has been regularly serviced, though it may require some minor mechanical attention or cosmetic touch-ups in the near future. Overall, it is a solid, honest car that gets you where you need to go without the price tag of a newer model.",
