    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new? You\u2019ve found it! This beauty is in absolutely pristine, mint condition\u2014it\u2019s been babied since day one and looks like it just rolled out of the showroom. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. Come see it for yourself, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
