    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in stunning shape\u2014seriously, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it garage-stored, and never missed a service. If you\u2019re looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve found it. Come take it for a spin, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This specimen boasts perfect compression across all cylinders and a recently serviced double-VANOS system. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory GKN limited-slip differential. Critically, the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the rod bearings have been replaced per preventative maintenance protocols. The suspension remains true to factory kinematics with fresh bushings and OEM dampers, providing unparalleled lateral grip and steering feedback. The exterior retains its original deep luster with zero evidence of panel gap misalignment or oxidation. This is a turn-key, investment-quality icon for the discerning purist.",
